        <Parent_String>gameboards (board game elements) [300136024], card, table and board game elements [300216609], recreational artifacts (equipment) [300218781], Recreational Artifacts (hierarchy name) [300136012], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
